---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout
  title="Botyoo for Agencies — Add Instagram DM Automation to Every Client Campaign"
  description="Botyoo gives agencies a white-label-friendly Instagram automation layer. Run funnels, capture leads, and prove ROI across all your clients — without adding headcount."
>
  <main class="pt-28 pb-28">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6">

      {/* Hero */}
      <section class="py-12 border-b border-border">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-3">
          For Agencies
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-foreground max-w-2xl leading-tight">
          Add Instagram DM automation to every client campaign.
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
          Botyoo gives agencies a white-label-friendly Instagram automation layer. Run funnels, capture leads, and prove ROI across all your clients — without adding headcount.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="https://app.botyoo.com/dashboard"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-foreground text-background px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-foreground/90 transition-colors"
          >
            Get started free
          </a>
          <a
            href="/pricing"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card text-foreground px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-muted/50 transition-colors"
          >
            See pricing
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* How it works */}
      <section class="py-14 border-b border-border">
        <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-12">
          How it works
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-20">

          {/* Step 1 */}
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <span class="flex items-center justify-center size-8 rounded-full bg-foreground/10 text-foreground text-sm font-bold">1</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide">Setup</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Set up client funnels in minutes</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                Duplicate proven templates across accounts. Each client gets their own flow, voice, and inbox — no bleed between workspaces. Onboard a new client in minutes, not days.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-card/80 ring-1 ring-foreground/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
              <p class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground mb-4">Client workspaces</p>
              <div class="space-y-2.5">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 rounded-lg bg-foreground/5">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="size-7 rounded-md bg-foreground/10 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-foreground/70 font-bold">NB</div>
                    <div>
                      <p class="text-xs font-medium text-foreground">NovaBrand Co.</p>
                      <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">4 active flows</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Live</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 rounded-lg bg-foreground/5">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="size-7 rounded-md bg-foreground/10 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-foreground/70 font-bold">PX</div>
                    <div>
                      <p class="text-xs font-medium text-foreground">Pixelwave Studio</p>
                      <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">2 active flows</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Live</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 rounded-lg bg-foreground/5">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="size-7 rounded-md bg-foreground/10 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-foreground/70 font-bold">GS</div>
                    <div>
                      <p class="text-xs font-medium text-foreground">GreenShift Foods</p>
                      <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Setup in progress</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-xs text-muted-foreground text-amber-400/80">Draft</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Step 2 */}
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="md:order-2">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <span class="flex items-center justify-center size-8 rounded-full bg-foreground/10 text-foreground text-sm font-bold">2</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide">Reporting</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Track what actually converts</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                See which posts drove DMs, how many leads were captured per flow, and which automations generated the most link clicks. Clean attribution data you can put directly into client reports.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-card/80 ring-1 ring-foreground/10 rounded-2xl p-6 md:order-1">
              <p class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground mb-4">Campaign analytics — NovaBrand Co.</p>
              <div class="space-y-3 text-xs">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3">
                  <div class="bg-foreground/5 rounded-lg p-3 text-center">
                    <p class="text-lg font-bold text-foreground">1,847</p>
                    <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-0.5">DMs sent</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-foreground/5 rounded-lg p-3 text-center">
                    <p class="text-lg font-bold text-foreground">643</p>
                    <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-0.5">Leads</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-foreground/5 rounded-lg p-3 text-center">
                    <p class="text-lg font-bold text-foreground">34.8%</p>
                    <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-0.5">CTR</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-1.5 pt-1">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span class="text-muted-foreground">Top flow</span>
                    <span class="text-foreground/70">Summer LINK post</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                    <span class="text-muted-foreground">Best open rate</span>
                    <span class="text-foreground/70">91.4%</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Step 3 */}
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                <span class="flex items-center justify-center size-8 rounded-full bg-foreground/10 text-foreground text-sm font-bold">3</span>
                <span class="text-xs font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wide">Management</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-3">Manage every account in one place</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                Switch between client workspaces from a single dashboard. Keep automations organized by client, share clean performance reports, and hand off accounts to team members without losing context.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-card/80 ring-1 ring-foreground/10 rounded-2xl p-6">
              <p class="text-sm font-medium text-foreground mb-4">Agency dashboard</p>
              <div class="space-y-3 text-xs">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-2.5 rounded-lg bg-foreground/5">
                  <div class="size-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
                  <span class="text-foreground flex-1">NovaBrand — Summer campaign</span>
                  <span class="text-muted-foreground">Active</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-2.5 rounded-lg bg-foreground/5">
                  <div class="size-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
                  <span class="text-foreground flex-1">Pixelwave — Product drop flow</span>
                  <span class="text-muted-foreground">Active</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-2.5 rounded-lg bg-foreground/5">
                  <div class="size-2 rounded-full bg-foreground/20"></div>
                  <span class="text-foreground flex-1">GreenShift — Lead gen setup</span>
                  <span class="text-muted-foreground">Draft</span>
                </div>
                <div class="border-t border-foreground/10 pt-2 flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-muted-foreground">Total leads this month</span>
                  <span class="text-foreground font-medium">2,184</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      {/* Use Cases */}
      <section class="py-14 border-b border-border">
        <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-8">
          Key use cases
        </h2>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-px bg-border border border-border rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
          <div class="bg-background p-5">
            <p class="font-semibold text-sm text-foreground">Creator campaign funnels</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1.5 leading-relaxed">Build comment-to-DM funnels for influencer campaigns. Every person who engages with a sponsored post becomes a capturable lead.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-background p-5">
            <p class="font-semibold text-sm text-foreground">Community management at scale</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1.5 leading-relaxed">Automate the repetitive inbox work — FAQs, link requests, story replies — so your team focuses on conversations that actually need a human touch.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-background p-5">
            <p class="font-semibold text-sm text-foreground">Paid-to-DM capture</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1.5 leading-relaxed">Run paid traffic to a post or story with a keyword CTA. Botyoo captures every responder as a lead — measuring paid-to-DM conversion directly.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-background p-5">
            <p class="font-semibold text-sm text-foreground">Bespoke AI flows per client</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-1.5 leading-relaxed">Configure Botyoo's AI to reply in each client's tone of voice. Superfan or luxury brand — the AI learns the personality and applies it consistently across every DM.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* FAQ */}
      <section class="py-14 border-b border-border">
        <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-8">
          FAQ
        </h2>
        <div class="divide-y divide-border" id="faq">
          <div class="faq-item py-4">
            <button type="button" class="faq-trigger w-full flex items-center justify-between text-left gap-4 text-sm font-medium text-foreground">
              Can I manage multiple client Instagram accounts from one Botyoo login?
              <svg class="faq-icon shrink-0 w-4 h-4 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-body hidden pt-3">
              <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Yes. Botyoo supports multiple workspaces, each tied to a separate Instagram account. You can switch between client workspaces from your dashboard without logging out. Each workspace has its own automations, contacts, and settings — fully isolated from others.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item py-4">
            <button type="button" class="faq-trigger w-full flex items-center justify-between text-left gap-4 text-sm font-medium text-foreground">
              How do I show clients ROI from DM automation?
              <svg class="faq-icon shrink-0 w-4 h-4 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-body hidden pt-3">
              <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Botyoo's analytics show DMs sent, link clicks, leads captured, and flow conversion rates per campaign. You can use this data to build client-facing reports. For deeper attribution, connect Botyoo to your tracking stack via webhooks and measure downstream conversions on your client's site.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item py-4">
            <button type="button" class="faq-trigger w-full flex items-center justify-between text-left gap-4 text-sm font-medium text-foreground">
              Can Botyoo match a client's specific brand voice?
              <svg class="faq-icon shrink-0 w-4 h-4 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-body hidden pt-3">
              <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Yes. Each workspace can be configured with custom AI instructions — tone, language, topics to avoid, and example responses. An upscale wellness brand and a streetwear label can both run Botyoo, and each will sound exactly like themselves in every DM. You write the rules; the AI follows them.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item py-4">
            <button type="button" class="faq-trigger w-full flex items-center justify-between text-left gap-4 text-sm font-medium text-foreground">
              Is Botyoo compliant with Meta's messaging policies for business accounts?
              <svg class="faq-icon shrink-0 w-4 h-4 text-muted-foreground transition-transform duration-200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-body hidden pt-3">
              <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Botyoo runs on Meta's official Messaging API, which means all automations operate within Instagram's permitted usage guidelines. We send DMs only to users who have opted in by initiating contact (commenting, using a keyword, or messaging first) — which is exactly what Meta's policies require for automated outbound messaging.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      {/* Bottom CTA */}
      <section class="py-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-6">
        <div>
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground">DM automation is the service your clients don't know they need yet.</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-1">Set up in under 5 minutes. No credit card needed.</p>
        </div>
        <a
          href="https://app.botyoo.com/dashboard"
          class="shrink-0 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-foreground text-background px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-foreground/90 transition-colors"
        >
          Start building free →
        </a>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach((item) => {
    item.querySelector('.faq-trigger')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const body = item.querySelector('.faq-body')
      const icon = item.querySelector('.faq-icon')
      body?.classList.toggle('hidden')
      icon?.classList.toggle('rotate-180')
    })
  })
</script>
